<ab facs="#facs_29_r1l22">vns heẅſlıch vnd auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>nym<ex>m</ex>er</expan> ſein . darcʒu ſint ſıe noch </ab>
